metadata.name: message #1
metadata.description:
It’s heartbreak for me as Energodar born be a Russian citizen living in Moscow and feels like I’am a hostage in my own country. To see how one bloody dictator crossed out the lives of a whole generation with absolutely mad war against Ukraine people.  

To support of place were I was born and in the name of the freedom to the place where I live.

 Peace to Ukraine
Freedom to Russia

1/1 edition 3500x3500 px.  

All $ETH funds will be donated to Nonprofit Organizations working in both countries
